{"tid":887151,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Lord 賓要坐監？？？","createTime":"2018-11-02T16:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T16:45:36.000Z","uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9327e757eed446bc693e1b6c99f2cfa430435265","tid":887151,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"Nicklas Bendtner appealing 50-day prison sentence for assaulting taxi driver.<br />\n<br />\nFormer Arsenal striker Nicklas Bendtner has been sentenced to 50 days in jail for assaulting a taxi driver.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://e2.365dm.com/18/11/768x432/skysports-nicklas-bendtner_4473776.jpg?20181102155521\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fe2.365dm.com%2F18%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskysports-nicklas-bendtner_4473776.jpg%3F20181102155521&h=b740314a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe 30-year-old, who plays for Norwegian club side Rosenborg, has been sentenced at a hearing in the Danish capital and was fined &pound;177.<br />\n<br />\nHis club told Danish media channel TV2 the sentence will not impact his future the club and his lawyers plan to appeal.<br />\n<br />\nBendtner was charged with beating and kicking a cab driver in Copenhagen on September 9. He admitted hitting the man but said he acted with self-defence after a quarrel over the fare.<br />\n<br />\nThe cab driver, whose jaw was broken, was acquitted of violence but fined &pound;350 for using his telephone while driving and not wearing his seatbelt."},{"pid":"e49601a11a91fcc2857456b3bd3834e7b947a933","tid":887151,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T16:04:08.000Z","msg":"@N_Bendtner"},{"pid":"29fad47da3b27e40d7041147caa4635976bfdaae","tid":887151,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T16:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceae7d84ce3b75df0bcd1db7b3495731035baae9","tid":887151,"uid":2033,"